      "span_text": "Indeed, only one study [CITATION_2] investigated the presence HPV infection and/or dysplasia in a small cohort of 31 SSc women; comparable frequencies of the virus versus healthy controls were noticed, but infection by 2 or more HPV types was 2 times more frequent in SSc patients."
